API Catalogs

Source: R/00-catalogs.R
catalogs.Rd

List of API catalogs:

  1. care - CMS Medicare API

  2. pro - CMS Provider API

  3. open - CMS Open Payments API

  4. caid - CMS Medicaid API

  5. health - CMS HealthCare.gov API

Usage

catalogs()

Value

<list> of catalogs

Examples

catalogs()
